# Credentials and secrets
.env
.env.*
!.env.template
*.key
*.pem
secrets/
credentials/

# User identity (Capa 5) — never versioned in upstream
**/working-memory.md
**/MEMORY.md
**/.claude/memory/
.claude/agents/!(esbirrillo|librarian|techy|reviewer).md

# User vault content
Vault/
!vault-template/
**/00. Inbox/*
**/01. Atomic Notes/*
**/02. Areas/*/!(_README.md|_TEMPLATE.md)
**/03. Sistema/templates/_user_*

# Logs
logs/
*.log
*.err.log
.claude/logs/
~/.hermes/logs/

# Python
